</p>
<p>In <code>battle.php</code> and <code>index.php</code>, we create a new <code>PDO</code> object. Let's have
<code>Container</code> do that instead. Create a new <code>public function getPDO()</code> inside
<code>Container</code>. Copy the code to make this and paste it here. Hmm, we need the
<code>$configuration</code> variable, so copy that from <code>bootstrap.php</code> and put it
here temporarily. Return <code>$pdo</code> at the bottom and perfect the method by
adding some PHPDoc:</p>
